nodes.text: Imperial Protocol Z-207 was a protocol of the Galactic Empire that was used by the Imperial Military. During a mission to Kashyyyk undertaken by Jedi Padawan Cal Kestis, an Imperial AT-AT pilot made contact with the All Terrain Armored Transport that Kestis had just hijacked. The pilot informed Kestis that he was in violation of the protocol and had to stand down, but was cut off by the droid BD-1.
